1.0.name: wordpress/page-menu-editor
1.0.description: This plugin gives you two additional inputs when Writing or Modifying a Static Page. One is for the page's menu label (anchor text), the other is for the title attribute within the link. By default there is no title attribute (as of 3.3). This plugin gives you more flexibility and will help to improve accessibility/usability.
